  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Weight loss may help psoriasis. Phototherapy helps psoriasis. Combining the two treatments
      may help even more. Determining if a high protein diet vs a low protein diet results in
      improving psoriais may help lead to future dietary effects on psoriasis therapy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
